TitleEnglish: Slam Dunk 2: National Domination! Sakuragi Hanamichi
SummaryEnglish: This is the second film from the series. It happens during Shohoku's 4th Round Qualifying game against Tsukubu High. The film features original characters including Godai, an old friend of Akagi and Kogure's, and Coach Kawasaki, a former pupil of Anzai-sensei.
Aliases: SLAM DUNK 全国制覇だ! 桜木花道
